All the speakers come, they
just want to talk to you.

00:21:48.370 --> 00:21:49.570 align:middle line:90%
Because you-- oh, brilliant.

00:21:49.570 --> 00:21:50.500 align:middle line:90%
Oh, what a good idea.

00:21:50.500 --> 00:21:51.010 align:middle line:90%
Oh, how wonderful.

00:21:51.010 --> 00:21:52.700 align:middle line:84%
And I've been with
you and your husband,

00:21:52.700 --> 00:21:55.150 align:middle line:84%
and you're just so
full of appreciation.

00:21:55.150 --> 00:21:56.110 align:middle line:90%
You're like a magnet.

00:21:56.110 --> 00:21:58.320 align:middle line:84%
You make men feel like, I
want to do more for you.

00:21:58.320 --> 00:21:59.710 align:middle line:90%
I want to give more for you.

00:21:59.710 --> 00:22:01.270 align:middle line:90%
So appreciation is one thing.

00:22:01.270 --> 00:22:02.950 align:middle line:84%
And women want to
be appreciated too.

00:22:02.950 --> 00:22:04.740 align:middle line:84%
And it will boost
their testosterone.

00:22:04.740 --> 00:22:05.740 align:middle line:90%
But generally speaking--

00:22:05.740 --> 00:22:07.198 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: If they accept it.

00:22:07.198 --> 00:22:09.490 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Either one, you don't
need as much testosterone

